I think this is better being a block template tag (e.g. `{% if_app_installed "reviews" %}`), like `iffeature` was, as filters are mostly used to transform the value.

Or at least a simple tag, which would be less code and more flexible, but require a bit more work to use:
```
{% is_app_installed "reviews" as reviews_app_is_installed %}
{% if reviews_app_is_installed %}
...
{% endif %}
```

